[Student "S"]
{NORTH opens 1\H with 17 points and five \Hs.

SOUTH, with 7 points and four trumps raises to 2\H.

NORTH has a mid-range hand, good enough to invite SOUTH to bid the game.

Too bad, but SOUTH is too weak to accept any invitations.}

